@nonni_io and @alex_lewin how would you feel if we just opened the invites up a bit more?

Last year, we were trying to keep it super focused and high signal. This year feels different. This year feels like we're just trying to show what a cool place this is to hang out and see hanging out here gets you involved in all this cool stuff.

I feel like the distance from the conference venue and mysterious location also act as a rate limiter.
